span.span: 《巴菲特致股东的信》

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left;

span.span: 价值投资的进化

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(98, 7, 3); text-align: left;

span.span: 巴菲特的投资哲学根植于其导师本杰明·格雷厄姆的价值投资，但又超越了格雷厄姆。他完成了从“购买便宜的普通公司”到“以合理价格购买伟大的公司”的伟大转变。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(98, 7, 3); text-align: left;

span.span: 1. 价格与价值的关系

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(98, 7, 3); text-align: left;

span.span: 这是巴菲特投资哲学的基石，也是对格雷厄姆思想的继承与发展。 "Price is what you pay. Value is what you get." (价格是你付出的，价值是你得到的。)

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(98, 7, 3); text-align: left;

span.span: 巴菲特强调，投资的成功与否并不取决于你买入后股票是否上涨，而在于你买入的企业其内在价值是否在持续增长。他提出了一个更深刻的观点： "It's far better to buy a wonderful company at a fair price than a fair company at a wonderful price." (以合理的价格买入一家伟大的公司，远胜于以便宜的价格买入一家平庸的公司。) 这标志着巴菲特投资思想的成熟，他将关注点从单纯的“便宜”转向了企业的“品质”。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(98, 7, 3); text-align: left;

span.span: 2. 市场先生与逆向思维

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(98, 7, 3); text-align: left;

span.span: 巴菲特频繁引用格雷厄姆的“市场先生”比喻，并将其逆向思维发挥到极致。 "Be fearful when others are greedy and greedy when others are fearful." (在别人贪婪时恐惧，在别人恐惧时贪婪。) 他认为，市场的非理性为理性的投资者创造了机会。投资者不应预测市场，而应利用市场的错误定价。市场的存在是为了服务投资者，而不是指导投资者。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;

span.span: 寻找伟大的企业

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: information-icon-font-family; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;

user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(97, 50, 4); text-align: left;

span.span: 1. 经济护城河 (Economic Moat)

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(97, 50, 4); text-align: left;

span.span: **无形资产**：如强大的品牌（可口可乐）、专利（制药公司）。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(97, 50, 4); text-align: left;

span.span: **成本优势**：拥有比竞争对手更低的生产或运营成本（GEICO保险）。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(97, 50, 4); text-align: left;

span.span: **转换成本**：用户从你的产品或服务切换到竞争对手那里时，需要付出高昂的代价（苹果生态系统）。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(97, 50, 4); text-align: left;

span.span: **网络效应**：用户越多，产品或服务就越有价值（美国运通）。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(97, 50, 4); text-align: left;

span.span: 2. 优秀的管理层

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(97, 50, 4); text-align: left;

span.span: 正直 (Integrity) ：管理层必须诚实可靠，将股东利益放在首位。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(97, 50, 4); text-align: left;

span.span: 智慧 (Intelligence)：管理层需要具备深刻的商业洞察力和行业知识。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(97, 50, 4); text-align: left;

span.span: 活力 (Energy) ：管理层应充满激情，致力于推动企业长期发展。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(97, 50, 4); text-align: left;

span.span: 此外，巴菲特尤其强调管理层的资本配置能力，认为这是CEO最重要的工作。优秀的管理者能像所有者一样思考，将每一分钱都投向能创造最大价值的地方。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(97, 50, 4); text-align: left;

span.span: 3. 业务可理解性 (Circle of Competence)

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(97, 50, 4); text-align: left;

span.span: 巴菲特坚持只投资于自己能够理解的“能力圈”内的企业。他认为，投资者不需要成为所有行业的专家，但必须对自己所投资的领域有深刻的理解。了解企业的商业模式、竞争格局和长期前景，是做出正确投资决策的前提。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(97, 50, 4); text-align: left;

span.span:
我的：核心投资于科技行业，尤其是是AI领域。
找到了支持的观点。

span.span: 4. 合理的价格

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(97, 50, 4); text-align: left;

span.span: 即使是伟大的公司，如果买入价格过高，也可能是一笔糟糕的投资。巴菲特会通过估算企业的“内在价值”（通常是其未来现金流的折现值），并与当前市值进行比较，以确保有足够的“安全边际”。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(97, 50, 4); text-align: left;

span.span: 这是个复杂的问题，还需要继续研究更多资料，才能合理预估哦

span.span: 经典语录精选

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(96, 82, 5); text-align: left;

span.span: "Rule No. 1: Never lose money. Rule No. 2: Never forget rule No. 1." (第一条原则：永远不要亏钱。第二条原则：永远不要忘记第一条。) "If you aren't thinking about owning a stock for 10 years, don't even think about owning it for 10 minutes." (如果你不打算持有一只股票十年，那就连十分钟都不要持有它。) "The business schools reward difficult complex behavior more than simple behavior, but simple behavior is more effective." (商学院奖励复杂困难的行为，但简单的行为更有效。)

span.span: 如果你有时间和兴趣研究公司，对你的投资回报将是非常有帮助的。

span.span: 核心投资概念词典

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(0, 102, 66); text-align: left;

span.span: 护城河 (Moat): 企业能够抵御竞争对手的持久性竞争优势。 内在价值 (Intrinsic Value): 一家企业在其生命周期内能够产生的现金流的折现值。 能力圈 (Circle of Competence): 投资者个人知识体系中能够深刻理解的领域或行业。 浮存金 (Float): 保险公司在收取保费和支付赔款之间，可以用于投资的资金。这是伯克希尔·哈撒韦成功的关键之一。 所有者收益 (Owner Earnings): 巴菲特提出的概念，指公司真实的、可供股东分配的现金流。计算公式为：净利润 + 折旧摊销 - 资本性支出。 资本配置 (Capital Allocation): 管理层如何分配公司资金（如再投资、并购、分红、回购）以实现股东价值最大化的决策过程。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left;

span.span: 长期主义的胜利

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(0, 18, 102); text-align: left;

span.span: 1. 复利的力量

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(0, 18, 102); text-align: left;

span.span: 巴菲特将复利誉为“世界第八大奇迹”。他的财富积累过程完美地诠释了复利的指数级增长效应。长期持有优质资产，让利润再投资，是实现财富巨大增值的关键。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(0, 18, 102); text-align: left;

span.span: 2. 永远持有的心态

span.span: "Our favorite holding period is forever." (我们最喜欢的持股期限是永远。) 这句话体现了巴菲特的终极长期投资心态。他购买股票时，是基于购买整个企业的思维，并假设股票市场明天就关闭，五年后再重新开放。这种心态能帮助投资者忽略短期市场波动，专注于企业的长期价值创造。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(0, 18, 102); text-align: left;

span.span: "Time is the friend of the wonderful business, the enemy of the mediocre." (时间是优秀企业的朋友，是平庸企业的敌人。)

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(0, 18, 102); text-align: left;

span.span: 企业换成人，也是一样的。

span.span: 风险的本质

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: information-icon-font-family; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;

user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(28, 26, 75); text-align: left;

span.span: **波动性不是风险**：传统金融学用贝塔系数（Beta）衡量风险，认为股价波动性越大风险越高。巴菲特认为，股价的短期波动是机会而非风险。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(28, 26, 75); text-align: left;

span.span: **真正的风险是永久性资本损失**：真正的风险来自于企业基本面的永久性恶化，或者投资者以过高的价格买入，导致无法收回本金。

div.style: user-select: none; --webkit-user-select:none; line-height: normal; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; overflow: visible; text-overflow: clip; white-space: break-spaces; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; font-family: NeverMind, sans-serif, "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft JhengHei", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(28, 26, 75); text-align: left;

span.span: **分散投资是对无知的保护**：对于不了解自己所投企业的投资者，分散是必要的。但对于真正了解企业的投资者，**集中投资**于少数几家最优秀的公司，风险反而更低，回报更高。

分散性并非普适最优的原则。
